Reports produced: 

Revocation of Nationality in Bahrain report (link: http://bahrainsalam.org/?p=651); 
Comparison of Bahrain's domestic legislation with International Standards; 

Activities: 

Participation in side events on Human Rights; 
Attend EU Parliament to examine latest developments; 
Attend UNHRC council; 
Cooperate with other NGOs to train Bahrainis, and produce reports and other literature; 
Pressure authorities to respect HR of victims adversely effected - usually by way of communication and social platform campaigns.
